<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15070</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹非常担心他的鼻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15071</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看起来很傻。蓝色小仙女笑了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么笑？”匹诺曹哭着问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在嘲笑你的谎言。”仙女说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当你说谎的时候，真的很容易被看穿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为每次你说谎，你的鼻子都会变长。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹感到很羞愧，他的脸变红了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50950</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起。”匹诺曹说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是从木偶师傅那里拿的金子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我爸爸不知道我去了剧院。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你发誓你会做一个乖孩子并尊重你的爸爸吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68211</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仙女在挥起魔杖前问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，我发誓！”匹诺曹说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蓝色小仙女挥动了一下魔杖，一只啄木鸟出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80634</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它把匹诺曹的鼻子啄成了原来的大小。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，监狱的栏杆消失了。匹诺曹爬出监狱，自由了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是回家的路。”仙女指着路说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你沿着这条路一直走，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你就会在天黑之前找到杰佩托的家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112827</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>记住你会做一个乖孩子的誓言，匹诺曹！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112828</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说完，她就飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，原来不听父母的话，结果会这么不好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从现在开始，我一定要认真做杰佩托要求我做的事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹边走边自言自语地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个小时后，匹诺曹觉得很饿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看到附近有一个葡萄藤。他决定向主人要点葡萄。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145012</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148878</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在穿过田地时，他掉进了一个陷阱里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148879</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，快来救救我！”匹诺曹叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159608</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊哈，我可算是抓到你了。”藏在附近的农民说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你就是那个经常偷鸡的小偷吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168338</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是的，先生，我没有偷你的鸡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176546</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拜托了，我只是想向你要一点葡萄吃，因为我真的很饿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176547</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊哈！你是想偷我的葡萄！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要给你点颜色看看！”他说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183605</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把匹诺曹从陷阱里面拽出来，并把他带回了家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>回到家，他在匹诺曹的脖子上面挂了一个铁链子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199144</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的看门狗今天早晨死了。”农民说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199145</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天晚上你就当我的狗，帮我看守我的鸡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208208</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>明天早晨我再决定怎么处置你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208209</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可怜的匹诺曹。他已经下定决心想要做一个乖孩子了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是农民并没有相信他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又饿又累。于是他爬进狗窝，睡着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个小时过去了，匹诺曹听到一些声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232484</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他向狗窝外望去。已经是晚上了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236208</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看到四只黄鼠狼站在鸡窝旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236209</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们是谁？”匹诺曹问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们停了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那你又是谁？”其中一只黄鼠狼问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245776</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的朋友奥斯卡在哪儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹猜奥斯卡一定是死去的那条狗，于是他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253628</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260774</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“奥斯卡今天早晨死了，我是新的看门狗。你们是谁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260775</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263559</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹又问了一遍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们是黄鼠狼，我们是来吃晚餐的。”其中一只黄鼠狼说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“奥斯卡是我们的朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279810</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你可以和奥斯卡一样跟我们做个交易。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279811</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个星期，我们都来这里。奥斯卡保证不会叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290811</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们会给奥斯卡一只鸡，然后带七只回家作为晚餐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你假装睡着了，我们也会留给你一只鸡。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在匹诺曹回答之前，那些黄鼠狼就钻进了鸡窝里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹关上了他们身后的门，然后开始大叫起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“汪！汪！汪！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314933</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>农民跑了过来，发现鸡棚里的黄鼠狼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314934</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“做得好！”他对匹诺曹说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你抓到了偷鸡贼！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥斯卡一定是太老了没能听到他们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹没有告诉农民奥斯卡和黄鼠狼做交易的事儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他只是点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>333264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>337854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你救了我的鸡，我会给你自由。”农民说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>337855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>341983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是首先，让我来给你做一顿早餐吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>341984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>348929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹开心地点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>